{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ak1.png?t=1728042903\" /><strong>Double the firepower! Local co-op update now live!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Two guns are always better than one. Dive into AK-xolotl's local co-op mode with a friend, battle through hordes of enemies, share epic power-ups, and blast through levels as a lethal duo of axolotls armed to the teeth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ak1.png?t=1728042903\" /><strong>AK-xolotl 2.0</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A massive update has arrived in AK-xolotl! Discover 20+ new weapons, new items, new biomes, and face off against new bosses and enemies. Major overhauls to the Axolittles, cooking, and weapon systems, plus the addition of weapon mods, bring new depth and variety to your axolotl adventures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ak-xolotl_together.jpg?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/line2.png?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">AK-xolotl is the <strong>ultimate</strong> top-down roguelite shooter starring the most adorable amphibian! You're an axolotl armed with an AK, that embarks on an epic rampage, shooting down anything that stands in your way. Slaughter your way through a variety of biomes and conquer randomly generated rooms, all while collecting delicious food and capturing precious baby Axolotls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_1.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Channel the incredible power of Axolotls' regeneration! If you're knocked down, you will rise again from the ashes and start stronger, unlocking new weapons with each fight. Fight, die, come back stronger and fight again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_2.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On your journey, you will find different baby Axolotls - Axolittles! Bring Axolittles back to your pond; nurturing them with love and care, they will grow up and become your next fighter with killer abilities! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_3.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From Slithering Sock Snakes to Giant (knife wielding) Enemy Crabs, these bosses will put your regenerative abilities to the test. Time to bring an AK-47 to a knife fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_5.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find Axolotl eggs and raise new powerful Axolittles by turning them into highly specialized little killing machines. Take their firepower to the next level by cooking up permanent, stat-improving recipes. Take no prisoners, eat everything and become unstoppable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_4.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight up close with the Axe-alotl or or set your Phaser to \u201cmurder\u201d... your playstyle is your pick! Take your firepower to the next level with mighty power-ups like Mjolnir, Gamer Juice or\u2026Cousin Carl?</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hello Pond","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/5263f1df36e843fcb5aab9598ea9210972825b35.jpg"},{"name":"The rampage begins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/51254decfb2e0ea9ea60ab152add97854a2e07ac.jpg"},{"name":"Gotta hatch 'em all","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/cb8461fd73b384c158569615e8e3607f57880954.jpg"},{"name":"They grow so fast...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/9f558d011cf83319cd12f83676871a8c1735365c.jpg"},{"name":"Happiness Farmer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/f26950c97fff3302463bf3e98d580f467ee9a6f9.jpg"},{"name":"Git gud","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/631004a53f4a80f5d527413e2b01d265b4956426.jpg"},{"name":"Capitalism 101","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/d4d318cae16c7e59744115bea55bab42e47cd5ad.jpg"},{"name":"Stonks","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/1199e6450cfc248a361235c2704fe8bfe5b90642.jpg"},{"name":"Bucket","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/ef54f9b3315c1e5f613fb1bd7de53e04afb2ed5a.jpg"},{"name":"Such a tryhard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1479140/a55b75fd5d0a4115ddb8fbe23f05bb79a7ed7089.jpg"}],"total":27},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728042903","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/page.bg.jpg?t=1728042903","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/9f2973ab494b4445a917d37cd04c2f5e6a5e48b0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728042903","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/9f2973ab494b4445a917d37cd04c2f5e6a5e48b0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728042903","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Trading Cards","id":29},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"This game contains blood splatters and violence toward animals in a cute 2D pixel art style.\r\n\r\nThe full version of the game will allow players to turn off blood and gore"},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>\ud83d\udc9aUpdate Roadmap\ud83d\udc9a</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_XOlotol_Release_Calendar_03.png?t=1728042903\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ak1.png?t=1728042903\" /><strong>Double the firepower! Local co-op update now live!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Two guns are always better than one. Dive into AK-xolotl's local co-op mode with a friend, battle through hordes of enemies, share epic power-ups, and blast through levels as a lethal duo of axolotls armed to the teeth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ak1.png?t=1728042903\" /><strong>AK-xolotl 2.0</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A massive update has arrived in AK-xolotl! Discover 20+ new weapons, new items, new biomes, and face off against new bosses and enemies. Major overhauls to the Axolittles, cooking, and weapon systems, plus the addition of weapon mods, bring new depth and variety to your axolotl adventures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ak-xolotl_together.jpg?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/line2.png?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">AK-xolotl is the <strong>ultimate</strong> top-down roguelite shooter starring the most adorable amphibian! You're an axolotl armed with an AK, that embarks on an epic rampage, shooting down anything that stands in your way. Slaughter your way through a variety of biomes and conquer randomly generated rooms, all while collecting delicious food and capturing precious baby Axolotls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_1.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Channel the incredible power of Axolotls' regeneration! If you're knocked down, you will rise again from the ashes and start stronger, unlocking new weapons with each fight. Fight, die, come back stronger and fight again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_2.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On your journey, you will find different baby Axolotls - Axolittles! Bring Axolittles back to your pond; nurturing them with love and care, they will grow up and become your next fighter with killer abilities! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_3.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From Slithering Sock Snakes to Giant (knife wielding) Enemy Crabs, these bosses will put your regenerative abilities to the test. Time to bring an AK-47 to a knife fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_5.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find Axolotl eggs and raise new powerful Axolittles by turning them into highly specialized little killing machines. Take their firepower to the next level by cooking up permanent, stat-improving recipes. Take no prisoners, eat everything and become unstoppable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/AK_Final_GIF_4.gif?t=1728042903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight up close with the Axe-alotl or or set your Phaser to \u201cmurder\u201d... your playstyle is your pick! Take your firepower to the next level with mighty power-ups like Mjolnir, Gamer Juice or\u2026Cousin Carl?</p>","developers":["2Awesome Studio"],"dlc":[2594170],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/header.jpg?t=1728042903","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a9 2023, Playstack and 2Awesome Studio, all rights reserved","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> MAC OS 11 Big Sur<br></li><li><stro